<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Verify Your Email</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rubik:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f5; font-family: 'Rubik', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: #111111;">
   <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 24px;">
        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; box-shadow:8px 8px 0px #000000;">
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ddd2;">
              <img
                                            src="https://cloudflare-b2.shrtchz.workers.dev/image3.png"

                      alt="Superfan"
                      width="150"
                      style="display:block; margin:0 ; max-width:150px; height:auto; border: 0;"
                    />
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-family: 'Rubik', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 700; color: #000000;">Verify your email</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 26px 26px 20px;">
              <div style="font-family: 'Rubik', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 700; color: #000000; margin: 0 0 12px;">
                Hello {{firstName}}
              </div>
              <div style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.45; color: #000000; margin: 0 0 18px;">
                Thanks for joining Superfan NG. Before we unlock the full experience for you, we just need to confirm this is really your email address. One click and you're verified.
              </div>
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border: 1px solid #d8cdbf; margin: 0 0 24px;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding: 14px 12px 12px;">
                    <div style="font-size: 7px; line-height: 1; color: #111111; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                      Confirm Your Email Address
                    </div>
                    <a href="{{verify_url}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #000000; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1; font-weight: 700; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                      Verify My Email
                    </a>
                    <div style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.35; color: #000000;">
                      This link expires in 10 minutes. Don't share it with anyone.
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <div style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.45; color: #000000; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                Didn't sign up for Superfan NG? You can safely ignore this email — nothing will change.
              </div>
              <div style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.45; color: #000000; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Need help? Shoot us an email at superfanng@superfan.ng
              </div>
              <div align="center" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 14px;">
                <div style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; color: #000000;">With love,</div>
                <div style="font-family: 'Rubik', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 700; color: #000000;">
                  The Superfan NG Team <img src="https://cloudflare-b2.shrtchz.workers.dev/love.png" alt="love" width="11" height="11" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border: 0;" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e8ddd2; margin: 0 0 10px;" />
              <div align="center" style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4; color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 4px;">
                © 2026 Superfan NG. All rights reserved.
              </div>
              <div align="center" style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4; color: #9ca3af;">
                You're receiving this email because you created a Superfan account.
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
